subproject.corporate outcome: Livelihoods and economic recovery generated, including infrastructure restoration, employment and sustainable income earning opportunities for crisis affected communities
subproject.description: The Private Sector Development components in this project are designed to establish the pillars necessary for the development of the private sector in Somalia through establishing the framework for regulatory, legal and institutional enabling environment; developing the financial sectors enabling policy environment and institutional capacity and supporting access to knowledge development through the Business Challenge Fund (BCF)
subproject.title: Private Sector Development
